title: Notable & Quotable: Stacey Abrams ‘I Did Not Challenge’ the Election
sub_head: ‘When I acknowledged I would not become governor, that he had won the election, I did not challenge the outcome of the election.'
body: MSNBC’s Rachel Maddow interviewing Stacey Abrams, Dec. 2. Ms. Abrams, a Democrat, lost the Georgia governor’s race in 2018 and announced Wednesday she’ll run again in 2022:
